<h3>While loops</h3>

<p>OCaml also provides a <code>while</code> loop, to execute some code
as long as an expression is true:</p>

<pre><code>while !x &gt; 20 do
  print_int !x; print_newline ();
  x := !x - 2
done</code></pre>

